title: Berkeley man identified as bicyclist killed in SF accident with Muni bus
text:
Photo: Gabrielle Lurie, Special To The Chronicle A bicyclist was struck and killed by a Muni bus on Market Street in San Francisco, California on Sunday, October 11, 2015. A bicyclist was struck and killed by a Muni bus on Market Street in...
A 47-year-old Berkeley man was identified Monday as a bicyclist struck and killed by a Muni bus on Market Street in San Francisco Sunday afternoon, according to the city medical examiner.
